{
  "stem": "3012.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when I took up French, I was very grateful for the four years in Latin, because it resembles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had German from home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I started to talk German when I-- when I began to talk Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in-- in Budapest I started to study French.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But life in Salgotarjan was-- if I can say this-- it was easy for a child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First of all, the loving background at home-- it was-- it was like paradise, all of these loving relatives at home, and my grandparents, and the aunts, and uncles, and the cousins.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And everybody rejoiced-- we rejoiced in each other as long as it lasted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Father was in business with the two brothers so mother-- mother stayed home and attended to the house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as long as I-- as I lived with them, of course, supervised everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schooling and whatever I was involved in she-- she knew about.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mother was a marvelous friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only a mother-- she was my best friend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was very good friends with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I really couldn't-- not even after all these years, there is absolutely nothing bad relating to the family that I could say.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- it-- it was really one of those exceptional good relations with-- with the family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a-- You mean apartment-- room-wise?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was in an apartment house not far from the factories.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was actually-- it-- it had a different layout, because when you-- when you walked in, you-- you were in a hall.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then you had the bathroom to the-- I can still see it, you know-- to the right, and the kitchen, and the pantry.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Hungary we had the pantry, not like a electric refrigerator like today.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
